Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:19.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,風好大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:20.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全入秋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:24.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:25.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到了有熱飲的季節了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,天地間已完全是一副秋天的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:43.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,季節流轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:46.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把我拋在後面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:49.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這在這
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:58.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前分配文化祭任務的時候你不是請假嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果就決定你負責舞台了 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:05.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,舞台…要做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:06.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:10.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搬東西的工作讓輕音部的人做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:14.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要負責時間安排之類輕鬆的事就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:15.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:21.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才叫你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:26.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:27.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就沒有職務空缺了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:33.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 安樂岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:44.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:02.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的婚禮決定在春假舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:42.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還體貼地親自過來告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:46.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:51.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回家路上 我們稍微聊了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥那傢伙 還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,活該
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼突然嚇了你一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 不啊 完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:08.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:12.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你很明顯地喜歡皆川老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你現在不戴眼鏡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 眼鏡壞了 順便就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,於是她就叫你戴隱形眼鏡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太明顯了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:34.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是比較喜歡你戴眼鏡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:36.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:42.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的哥哥會讓我想起過去的他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口…稍微有點痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,婚禮你能來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是肯定的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:19.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:35.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是正式表演最終版的時間表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你們這兩天一直準備肯定很累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}在就位前可以自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}但也請掌握好時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,超有領導風範啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對這個舞台工作她可是相當賣力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那裡的男生A、B
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:54.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要是敢遲到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:56.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信我把你們丟進後夜祭的火堆裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總算做得差不多了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他來接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要和男友逛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:06.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 沒時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:12.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事 感覺有點累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們去哪休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:19.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}想去個安靜點的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那先吃點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:19.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要和誰待在一起什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然腦海裡浮現出幾個選項
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是打消了這個念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:26.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,從哪裡逛起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先去吃點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:33.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,距離就位還有些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:39.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡正在舉行時裝秀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請過來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多很棒的作品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:44.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}慢死了 你去幹嘛了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:46.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 不然就要結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:27.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我對麥的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比你更長久 更真實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我現在痛快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也試著自己邁出腳步就能明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:56.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你很棒哦 歐端同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,刺繡太精細了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是你自己做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成你平時穿的衣服也是手工做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:06.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前就想問問看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 下次教我製作方法吧 乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:15.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫最可…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也教教我吧 乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:17.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫最可啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:19.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:22.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了 安樂岡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快去幫大伙的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要搬哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快點動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:35.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡同學 幫忙拿一下線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:38.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉安樂岡同學 幫忙發個傳單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡 把那裡的器材搬到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪…哪個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:49.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個！快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:08:59.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:05.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:12.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人自在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:16.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人能想清楚很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:20.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就是一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕孤身一人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:30.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:34.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是孤單的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:39.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那這種事也沒有意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:46.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:50.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:55.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在那天許下了約定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀好僵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:27.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:37.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會相遇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:51.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 願意幫忙的人結業式以後都到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:56.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:59.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是慶祝老師的結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要做這麼多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:04.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別講話 做事乾脆點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:05.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是執行小組的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:09.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 把那邊不用的工具搬到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 還要搬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡同學 我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫森山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今年開始跟你同班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:43.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 安樂岡同學 快點把東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:45.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…安樂岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你和粟屋怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這段時間都沒看見你跟他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…安樂岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話 請跟我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能不要隨便在這裡秀存在感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:20.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:31.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:39.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 剛才只是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:56.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:01.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你暫時還不想被他人告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\bord0\fn@方正卡通_GBK\fs90\c&H9237E4&\fad(200,0)\pos(710,549.8)}流-------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:13.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好溫柔 小繪好溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好我知道了 先擦一下鼻涕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你再也不會和我說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:25.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:29.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 花了點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你剪頭髮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:41.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你是入學考試那時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天沒有綁辮子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我能摸摸看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮好順滑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:57.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放下來果然是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那時不知為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有種被接納的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿就像第一次開始呼吸一般
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,世界接納了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:15.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:20.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:26.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個髮型也很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:35.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,清爽多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord1.05}祝鐘井老師 皆川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord1.05\an7}結婚快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不啊 真害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們一起寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:11.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:12.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:16.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡同學會去老師們的婚禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:22.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 我還沒去過結婚典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:24.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:34.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和最喜歡的人白頭偕老
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:38.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,扔  花 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnArial\pos(919.2,993)}bouquet toss
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:10.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,扔什麼 不是沒扔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:11.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,收下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:13.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:14.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知…知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下次 可不能被搶走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:30.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用你說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的約定也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,堆疊的日子也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經失去了意義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最初也只是寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以相濡以沫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:09.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一心思念著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:11.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的熱心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:15.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:22.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們曾經交換的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:26.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在情場失意的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:31.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 約定已經失效了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:37.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新的契約要重新締結
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H3A3A38&\fad(300,0)\frz347.7\blur1.5\pos(1336.8,640.601)}抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:40.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:45.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別道歉 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:02.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,事先說明 茜姐變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:03.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:08.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最後還是選擇了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:14.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:18.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是很喜歡哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:23.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正兰亭宋_GBK\frz270\bord0\fad(500,1000)\c&H000000&\b1\pos(1033.8,567)}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說出口也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:33.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:42.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到我們第一次迴避了身體接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:52.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,選擇了用語言來安慰對方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:56.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是至今都沒做過的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說了各式各樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:01.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,連直到現在的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:10.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺 真漫長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,初戀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:15.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說初戀是無法實現的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:22.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是秋天 卻突然覺得很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:27.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,照亮著塵埃 空氣緩緩流動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:31.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有著舊木頭的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,時間永恆地一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:38.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我靜靜地深吸一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下定了決心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:00.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇到麥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:05.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在尋求著真正的那一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚知道這是無法輕易入手的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:22.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼許願怎麼祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能觸碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:29.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下次會受更重的傷也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:35.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會更加地孤獨也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:40.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續追尋著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:49.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:50.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想分開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:51.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想放手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:54.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想留下你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想完結
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想你留下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:01.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:03.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:11.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使現在得不到救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還在尋找著真正的那一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:19.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:49.36,Kuzu_title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs82.5\frz270\bord0\c&H28262B&\b1\pos(708,774)\blur15\alpha&HF0\t(0,3400,1.5,\blur0\alpha&H00&)}兩人的故事
